<li id="cite_note-laureat_nobel_1984-1"><span class="mw-cite-backlink noprint">↑ <sup><a href="#cite_ref-laureat_nobel_1984_1-0">a</a> et <a href="#cite_ref-laureat_nobel_1984_1-1">b</a></sup> </span><span class="reference-text"><abbr class="abbr indicateur-langue" title="Langue : anglais">(en)</abbr> <span class="citation not_fr_quote" lang="en">«&#160;<span class="italique">for their decisive contributions to the large project, which led to the discovery of the field particles W and Z, communicators of weak interaction</span>&#160;»</span> <i>in</i> Personnel de rédaction, «&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/physics/laureates/1984/"><i>The Nobel Prize in Physics 1984</i></a>&#160;», <a href="/wiki/Fondation_Nobel" title="Fondation Nobel">Fondation Nobel</a>, 2010. Consulté le 23 juin 2010</span>
